                                Microdermabrasion is being labeled the “instant facelift” and has become increasingly popular amongst those that want a youthful, glowing complexion.  Unlike other more invasive procedures such as Botox and plastic surgery, this revolutionary treatment is safe, affordable and pain-free; with no recovery time.  No chemicals used and can be done quickly and easily on your lunch hour!  The process is very affordable and quite a bit less expensive than other skin-resurfacing treatments.  The promising cosmetic procedure is becoming a favorite as a result of its low cost and convenience for people with busy lifestyles.  Although the popularity is mostly among women, men are enjoying the benefits of having healthy skin too.
                            </p>
